APEX CODE TO DISPLAY NUMBER OF DAYS IN MONTH
============================================================

public class basic 
{
    public static void base()
    {
        integer days = date.daysInMonth(2022,7);
        system.debug('TOTAL NO OF DAYS IN MONTH : ' +days);
        
    }
        

}

============================================================

TO EXECUTE OUTPUT USE THE FOLLOWING COMMAND

basic.base();
============================================================
